item.title: About
item.description:
$whoami

I am a highschool student, interested in computers. I promote the use of free and open source software. I have deep interest towards computer science. I like tinkering around in my linux desktop, from wasting my time to configuring the shit out of it, to learning many new things daily.

item.title: Support
item.description:
Want to support me?

Well, you can subscribe to my youtube channel. And help me with active projects in my github.
